{"tid":2098082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎未平  中国又爆發鼠疫   CNN：吃老鼠染病恐人傳人","createTime":"2020-07-07T08:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T11:25:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0aaab29b2a3cbaf968e7171d070507afa82a56","tid":2098082,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情未見緩和，中國內蒙古近日又爆發鼠疫，患者若不及時接受治療恐惡化至肺炎性鼠疫，當局現已發布警告，專家指出，肺炎性鼠疫具有人傳人的特性，若疫情擴散恐引起大規模流行。<br />\n<br />\n根據《CNN》報導，內蒙巴彥淖爾市烏拉特中旗溫鎮近日傳出鼠疫確診案例，當局現已對該地區發布鼠疫疫情Ⅲ級預警通告，持續至今年底，據稱，鼠疫在該地區一直未曾滅絕，原因是當地存在大量的土撥鼠，被民眾視為桌上佳餚，因而確保了與感染源的經常性接觸。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，本次爆發的確診案例屬三種鼠疫中的腺鼠疫，又稱淋巴腺鼠疫，未治療下的死亡率高達3至9成，不過若接受適當治療則可降至1成，在中世紀歐洲造成近半數人口死亡的黑死病便是此疾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3220449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3220449&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettiva%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=af461d35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3220449&h=9695da15\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3220449</a>"},{"pid":"29f40db48dbfa89459903ed2cff96d81eab21dd0","tid":2098082,"uid":130901,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"仆街梁美芬"},{"pid":"06d07094df907b216143a2a5b788e64f3d2b9554","tid":2098082,"uid":349872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"支那人真係咩狗屎垃圾都放得入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31b78eb44e20e60e75ebb720a840015ef4d330c","tid":2098082,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb592d7211